title: About Me
text:
I am currently finishing my final semester as a graduate student at UMass Amherst studying Data Analytics and Computational Social Science (DACSS). I previously received a bachelor’s degree in psychology from UMass Lowell in May 2022. When I was an undergraduate student, I enjoyed my classes on research and statistics, and I wanted to continue studying these topics in graduate school, which led me to the DACSS program at UMass Amherst.
For more information on my educational and professional experience, my resume can be viewed here.
